text:
Toh Chaliye Shuru karte hai !!

ye toh yaad nahi first time baat kab , kahan aur kese hui bas itna yaad ki starting Summer of code and Pubg se hui thhi . Tumne introduce karwaya game se . Uske baad toh pubg ki jo chull machi Bhai Sahi me mza aa gya . Abhi toh time nahi lekin jab free hounga tab sath me firse pubg khelenge . Aur tumko hacks ki aadat lagwaaunga  . 

Aur Bhai CSE ke courses me jo bakchodiya kri tumne bhai ek number !! . Tumko dekh dekh ke hum bhi thoda bhot "Googling" seekh gye . result tumhare saamne hai "A" lge hai sirf Google karke. 

Bro, I have spent my most of the time with you BC itna zyada kar liya ki mera baat karne ka style chance ho gya hai . Mere school ke friends bolte hai ki , "Bhai tu kabse itna sober ho gya?" ,"abe tu kabse "tum" ka use karne lga?". Ab unko kya hi jawab du mujhe khud pta nahi lga kab ho gya aisa . 

Trading  ki chull bhi tumne hi lagwai . BC iss chakkr me Saala trading BOT code kar diya , Trading bhi seekh li. Bas tum jaldi se mastercard me jao payments , databases etc ka sab seekh lo . Full Team ready hai . Fir compound interest lagayenge , ICO lenge aur bhot kuch hai aage . Fir Saath me gaayenge "PUMP IT , DUMP IT ! " . 

Aur bhai UK trip ultimate . Uss trip me sab kuch apne aap set beth gya . Again "COINCIDENCE" . Dobara Chalange trip pe aur baar drive me karunga aur haan choice of place bhi meri hogi ( most probably somewhere in West ) .  Tab tak Chill kro , Girlfriend banao , Exercise karo aur fast-food kam kha kya Bc din bhar Lays khaata rehta hai .
author: Hemant  Kumar
